snippet.title: The Immortal gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for The Immortal, Dos PC game produced by Electronic Arts in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/the-immortal/4385/
Exploring a dark trap-laden dungeon in this fantasy roleplaying adventure.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
